01:29:22.225 --> 01:29:26.827
Sutra imam susret s pravim liječnikom.

01:29:30.565 --> 01:29:33.367
Znaš li koji je najgori dio?

01:29:35.671 --> 01:29:38.973
Nitko neće biti
tu da me isprati.

01:29:44.446 --> 01:29:47.113
U svakom slučaju

01:29:48.183 --> 01:29:51.385
bilo je ugodno razgovarati
s tobom, Amanda.

01:29:53.321 --> 01:29:55.789
Također, Jack.

01:31:58.313 --> 01:32:00.981
Kažem vam, on je
jedan gadan kurvin sin.

01:32:00.983 --> 01:32:04.051
On unajmljuje mlade, on plača više
